data.description: Oversized corner lot Captivating potential! Step into this utterly beautiful 3 bedroom 2 bath home located in the desirable Harbor Heights area. Set atop an oversized corner lot, this abode has been through several updates done by the current owners. The kitchen has new cabinets, granite countertops, tile backsplash, and appliances. Both bathrooms have been updated and include new vanities, fixtures, and tile. The master bathroom also features a new stunning walk-in shower. New tile throughout offers easy upkeep and comfort. This home also has two screened-in lanais for added outdoor space and a 12x24 shed with built in cabinets, shelves, and a loft on each side for added storage. But that's not all. This home also comes with hurricane shutters, a new roof from 2014 and new septic, A/C, and water heater in 2021. Enjoy the multiple upgrades and other added extras that come with this stunning house. Also conveniently located in a non-deed restricted waterfront community, close to Harbour Heights Park where you can enjoy boat ramps, day docks, playground, pavilions, barbecue areas, basketball, shuffleboard, and lighted tennis courts with no HOA fees. Just 5 mins from I-75 entrance at exit 167, enjoy easy access to nearby cities like Venice, Sarasota, Fort Myers, and Naples. Schedule a showing today to experience this captivating potential and make this wonderful house your home!
